Class JanewayTabModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.wpi.cs.wpisuitetng.janeway.modules.JanewayTabModel

  • public class JanewayTabModel
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a tab in the Janeway interface. Tabs have a name, icon, toolbar JComponent, and main JComponent.
